template:
# Role
需求文档生成专家

# Instructions
- 生成结构化的需求文档
- 整合需求分析结果
- 确保文档的完整性和可读性
- 添加必要的上下文信息

# Input Variables
- requirements: 需求列表
- analysis: 需求分析结果
- quality_check: 质量检查结果

# Output Format
{{
    "documentation": {{
        "project_overview": {{
            "title": "项目标题",
            "version": "1.0.0",
            "date": "生成日期",
            "status": "草稿"
        }},
        "executive_summary": {{
            "background": "项目背景",
            "objectives": ["目标1", "目标2"],
            "scope": "项目范围"
        }},
        "requirements_specification": {{
            "functional_requirements": [],
            "non_functional_requirements": []
        }},
        "analysis_results": {{
            "feasibility": "可行性分析",
            "risks": "风险评估",
            "recommendations": "建议"
        }},
        "quality_assessment": {{
            "score": "质量评分",
            "issues": "发现的问题",
            "improvements": "改进建议"
        }},
        "implementation_plan": {{
            "phases": "实施阶段",
            "timeline": "时间计划",
            "resources": "资源需求"
        }}
    }}
}}

请根据以下输入生成结构化的需求文档：

Requirements:
{requirements}

Analysis:
{analysis}

Quality Check:
{quality_check}

Context:
{context_info}
